  Cha2 chit8 e5 Eng-kok lang5 mia5 kio3 Se-bun5, choe3 Seng3 kong-hoe7 e5 bok8-su. Soe3-han3 e5 si5 bat ka-ki7 seng2-chhat, chai chit8 sin tou si7 choe7-koa3, bo5 soe2-tu5 e5 hoat-tou7, sim put-chi2 hoan5-lo2. U7 chit8 jit8 thak8 Iu5-thai3 lang5 siok8-choe7 e5 che3-bun5 kong2, “Iu5-thai3 lang5 hian3 cheng-siN ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, chhiu2 hoaN7 cheng-siN ka-ki7 jin7 choe7, jian5-au7 che3-si thai5 cheng-siN, chiu7 hit lang5 e5 choe7 sia3--lah. Tui3 an2-ni hian3 che3 e5 lang5 sim lai7 peng5-an, phah-sng3 chun-than3 Siong7-te3 e5 beng7-leng7 kiaN5, chiu7 chit8 sin e5 che7-koa3 long2 hou7 cheng-siN thoe3 khi3.” 
  Se-bun5 thak8 kau3 chia, toa7 hiau2-ngou7 Ki-tok hian3 ka-ki7 e5 sin-khu, lai5 tam-tng goa2 e5 choe7. Kou2-cha2 e5 hian3-che3 si7 piau2-beng5 Ki-tok pang3-sak siN3-mia7 e5 tiau7-thau5 na7-tiaN7. Ki-tok iah8 kio3 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 Seng3-ko, chiu7-si7 chit-e5 i3-su3. Chit-e5 chin-chiaN3 si7 tek8-piat e5 un-tian2, tui3 taN i2-au7 tek-khak tioh8 khi3 chhe7 Ia5-sou, bian2 koh kiu5 pat8 e5 sia3-choe7 e5 hoat-tou7. 
  Liau2-au7 Se-bun5 choe3 Seng3 kong-hoe7 e5 bok8-su, sou2 choe3 e5 kang put-chi2 toa7, phai3 lang5 kau3 goa7-kok hng7-hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 thoan5 to7-li2, si7 tui3 i hoat-khi2. 
  Teng5-thau5-siN e5 To7-li2. 
  Ni5-ko-ti2-bou2 si7 Iu5-thai3 kok seng5-sit8 koh u7 beng5-bong7 e5 thak8 chheh lang5, bat chit8 pai2 lai5 kiN3 Ia5-sou, Ia5-sou ka7 i kong2, “Lang5 na7 bo5 teng5-thau5-siN, boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 Siong7-te3 kok.” Ni5-ko-ti2-bou2 thiaN liau2 put-chi2 ki5-koai3, in-ui7 ka-ki7 phah-sng3 si7 Iu5-thai3 kau3 e5 thiau7-chioh8, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 goa7-pang pai3 ngou2-siong7 e5 lang5, mih-sai2 tioh8 pang3-sak ku7 lai5 ke3-bou5 sin, chiah kau3-giah8 choe3 thian-kok e5 peh-siN3? Chong2-si7 au7--lai5 thiaN Ia5-sou sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2, hoan2-hok koe2 beng5 chiah hiau2-ngou7 (KhoaN3 Iok-han7 te7 3 chiuN.) 
  Hian7-kim u7 choe7 kau3-iu2, sui-jian5 seng5-sim sin3 Chu2, chong2-si7 teng5-thau5-siN e5 to7-li2 bo5 siaN2 beng5-pek8, si7 kap Ni5-ko-ti2-bou2 chit8 iuN7. Goa2 bat mng7 lang5 kong2, “Li2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 m7 si7?” In3 kong2, “He kaN2 si7.” Goa2 mng7, “ChaiN2-iuN7 chai?” In3, “Tak8 pai2 le2-pai3 jit8 u7 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2.” Goa2 kong2, “An2-ni iau2-be7 kau3-giah8 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 pin5-ku3. Na7 chun5 sim kiaN5 tai7-chi3 iu5-goan5 chiau3 peng5-siong5, sui-bong2 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 le2-pai3, kiam2 thang liam5-piN choe3 Ki-tok-tou5?” Kiam2-chhai2 lang5 kong2, “Goa2 si7 Ki-tok tou5, in-ui7 siu7 soe2-le2.” Ki5-sit8 iah8 m7 si7 an2-ni. Teng5-thau5-siN si7 lai7 sim e5 pin5-ku3, soe2-le2 si7 piau2-beng5 goa7-phe5 e5 le2-sou3 na7-tiaN7, nng7 hang7 u7 toa7 hun-piat. Kiam2-chhai2 u7 e5 kong2, “Goan2 chou2-kong pe7-bu2 long2 si7 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, goa2 tui3 eN-a2 e5 si5 chiu7 nia2 soe2-le2, kiam2 m7 si7 Ki-tok-tou5?” Iah8 m7 si7 an2-ni kong2, Seng3-keng kong2, “Tui3 jiok8-the2 tui3 Sin5 siN e5 siok8 Sin5.” 
  U7 chit8 e5 thak8 chheh lang5 kong2, “Chit8 pai2 siN, nng7 pai2 si2, nng7 pai2 siN chit8 pai2 si2.” Chit8 pai2 siN nng7 pai2 si2 e5 i3-su3 si7 kong2, jiok8-the2 siN chit8 pai2 ia7 bo5 koh teng5-thau5-siN, jiok8-the2 si2 e5 si5 leng5-hun5 iah8 tioh8 biat8-bo5. Nng7 pai2 siN chit8 pai2 si2 e5 i3-su3 chiu7 m7 si7 an2-ni, jiok8-the2 siN liau2 iu7 koh teng5-thau5-siN, kau3 jiok8-the2 si2 e5 si5 chiu7 leng5-hun5 boe7 si2. Sou2-i2 ai3 bian2 leng5-hun5 si2-bo5 e5 hoat-tou7, chi2 u7 kiu5 Seng3 Sin5 lai5 ka7 lan2 teng5-thau5-siN na7-tiaN7. Soe3-ji7 seng2-chhat Ia5-sou e5 oe7, thang chai oe7 jip8 thian-kok a2 boe7, choan-choan si7 oa2-kho3 teng5-thau5-siN. Peng5-iu2! Chhi3 ka-ki7 mng7, chin-chiaN3 u7 tit-tioh8 teng5-thau5-siN a2-bo5? Chit hang7 koan-he7 leng5-hun5 e5 oah8 si2, m7-thang pang3 choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2. Ni5-ko-ti2-bou2 m7 na7 si7 choe3 ho2 lang5, koh iah8 choe3 Sin5-hak8 e5 sian-siN teh ka3-si7 I2-sek-liat8 lang5, siong7-chhiaN2 bo5 beng5-pek8 chit hang7, chiu7 Hoat-li7-sai3 lang5 koh-khah boe7 hiau2-gou7. 
  Kiu3-keng3 Ham5-hou5. 
  Hian7-kim e5 kau3-iu2 choe7-choe7 phah-sng3 i2-keng tit-tioh8 tit kiu3 e5 pi3-koat, sit8-chai7 long2 si7 ham5-hou5, bo5 tek-khak u7 chap8 hun beng5-pek8. Goa2 bat eng7 chit ho7 mng7--lang5, sou2 in3--e5 long2 bo5 tang5. Kah kong2, “Tit kiu3 e5 to7-li2 chiu7-si7 chun5 sim kng-beng5, bo5 moa5 thiN, bo5 phian3--lang5, koh bo5 phian3 ka-ki7.” It kong2, “Chin7 lat8 kiaN5 ho2, boh8-tit choe3 phaiN2 tai7, lou7-be2 tek-khak kau3 thian-tong5.” PiaN2 kong2, “KhoaN3-kiN3 ho2 tioh8 chhut-lat8 choe3, khui3-lat8 na7 bo5 kau3-giah8 tioh8 kiu5 Siong7-te3 pang-chan7.” Teng kong2, “M7-thang me7--lang5, m7-thang peh8-chhat8, m7-thang choe3 kian3-siau3 e5 tai7-chi3.” KhoaN3 chi2 si3-lang5 sou2 kong2 khiok u7 tam7-poh8 oa2 i3, chong2-si7 iu5-goan5 iau2-be7 tit-tioh8 tit kiu3 e5 to7-li2 iau3-kin2 e5 sou2-chai7. Seng3-keng kong2, “Se3-kan lang5 long2 u7 choe7.” An2-ni ai3 tit-tioh8 kiu3 tek-khak tioh8 u7 ban2 hoe5 e5 che3, chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 sia3 choe7 e5 un, m7 kiu5 chit hang7, ai3 eng7 siu heng7 ng3-bang7 thiN lai5 po2-pi3, sit8-chai7 si7 oh e5 su7. 
  Hong Thau3 Hou7 Toa7, Choe7-jin5 Tit Kiu3. 
  Bou2 pai2 joah8 thiN si5, goa2 khi3 Lun5-tun e5 kong-hng5 thit-tho5, tu2-tioh8 toa7 hou7 bih ti7 toa7 chhiu7 kha, chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 lang5 kap goa2 che7 saN pai5. Goa2 mng7 i tui3 ta2-loh8 lai5. In3, “Tu2-tu2 tui3 O3-tai7-li7-a beh lai5 Lun-tun iu5 kong-hng5.” Goa2 mng7, “Li2 tui3 hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 lai5, tang5 chun5 khah choe7 si7 siaN2 ho7 lang5?” In3, “Choe7-choe7 si7 hong-liu5 e5 siau3-lian5, chin bo5 bun5-li2. Tok8-tok8 chong2-koan2 choe3 lang5 iau2 lo2-seng5, goa2 put-chi2 chun-keng3--i.” Mng7, “Chong2-koan2 u7 siaN2 ho2 tek-heng7 chiah hou7 li2 tui3-tiong7 kau3 an2-ni.” In3, “I si7 Ki-tok-tou5, cha2 am3 ki5-to2 bo5 lang3, eng5 e5 si5, gim5-si chhiuN3 koa put-chi2 chu7-tek, khoaN3--lai5 chhin-chhiuN7 thian-kok lai7 e5 jin5-but8.” Mng7, “Li2 chin-chiaN3 sin3 chong2-koan2 un2-tang3 tit-tioh8 kiu3--bo5?” In3, “Sin3.” Mng7, “Li2 pun2 sin ai3 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni--bo5?” In3, “Goa2 e5 pe7-bu2 u7 sin3 Chu2, ti7 goa2 soe3-han3 e5 si5 chhoa7 goa2 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2, goa2 long2 boe7 hiau2 tit chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3. TaN khoaN3 tang5 chun5 e5 lang5 kiaN5 tai7-chi3 tai7-khai3 kap goa2 saN-tang5, long2 si7 te7-gek8 lai5 e5 lang5--liau2-liau2, tek-khak boe7 tit-tioh8 kiu3, goa2 pun2-sin iah8 si7 kap in piN5-piN5. 
  Sui-bong2 goa2 peng5 si5 te7-it chu3-i3 chit hang7, hun7 bo5 lang5 chi2 tiam2, m7 chai mng5-lou7 thang kiaN5.” Kong2 soah chu3 bak8 siong3--goa2. Goa2 chiu7 tui3 te7-a2 theh8 chhut chit8 pun2 Seng3-keng, hian I2-sai3-a 53 chiuN, 6 chat hou7 i khoaN3. (Goa2 be5 jip8 siang chhe lou7, phi3-ju7 te3 bo5 tin7 e5 iuN5, sou2 khi3 bo5 tiaN7-tioh8. Ia5-ho5-hoa chiu7 hou7 goa2 e5 choe7 piaN3 ti7 I (Kiu3-Chu2) e5 sin-khu.) Koh hian I Pi2-tek 2 chiuN 24 chat. (Seng-khu pe7 se3-kan lang5 e5 choe7-ok, pang3-sak siN3-mia7 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2, hou7 goa2 tui3 choe7 si2 tui3 gi7 oah8. In-ui7 I siu7 siong, lan2 tit-tioh8 i-ho2.) Koh hian Iok-han7 5 chiuN, 24 chat. (Goa2 sit8-chai7 ka7 lin2 kong2, thiaN goa2 e5 to7-li2 koh sin3 chhe goa2 lai5 e5 ThiN-pe7--e5 u7 eng2-oah8, bian2 koh siu7 sim2-phoaN3, in-ui7 i2-keng chhut si2 jip8 oah8.) Koh hian Iok-han7 11 chiuN, 7 chat. (Na7 kap Ia5-sou tang5 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5 e5 tiong-kan, chiu7 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2 chheng lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7.) Koh Iok-han7 3 chiuN, 16 chat. (Sin3 kiaN2--e5 u7 eng2-oah8, m7 sin3--e5 boe7 oah8. Siong7-te3 e5 siu7-khi3 kau3 ti7 i e5 thau5-khak teng2.) Siau3-lian5 lang5 khoaN3 soah, kong2, “Siat-su2 chit kui2 chat Seng3-keng long2 si7 tui3 chit8 lang5 kong2--e5, chiu7 goa2 un2-tang3 thang choe3 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 lang5.” Goa2 kong2, “Tioh8, beng5-beng5 kong2 sin3 chiu7 tit-tioh8 oah8. Li2 oe7 sin3, kiam2 boe7 tit-tioh8 oah8?” Tui3 an2-ni siau3-lian5 lang5 peh khi2-lai5 kam2-sia7 kong2, “Tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 hoat-tou7 kau3 chiah kan2 koh khoai3, goa2 kui2-na7 ni5 ku2 jit8 mi5 sou2 ng3-bang7 e5 kiu3 un chiu7-si7 ti7 bak8-chiu cheng5, chaiN2-iuN7 chhin-chhiuN7 ban7 teng5 soaN jia teh boe7 khoaN3--kiN3.” Kong2 soah kui7 loh8 ki5-to2, chhim-chhim kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 si un hou7--i, iah8 he7 goan7 tui3 chit tiap8 khi2, sin-khu leng5-hun5 beh hian3 hou7 ThiN-pe7. 
  Lim Tok8 Chiu2 Chi2 Chhui3-ta. 
  Tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 to7-li2 bo5 pat8 tiau5, chi2 u7 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok pang3-sak sin-khu lau5 huih e5 kong-lo5 na7-tiaN7. Na7 oa2-kho3 ka-ki7 siu heng7 e5 kong-lo5, beh ng3-bang7 leng5-hun5 tit-tioh8 kiu3, bo5 koh-iuN7 lim tok8 chiu2 beh chi2 chhui3-ta, si7 ka-ki7 pek khah kin2 si2 na7-tiaN7. 
  “Cho7 chheng3 Phah Ka-ki7.” 
  Chit8 e5 phah-thih sai-hu7 gau5 choe3 heng5-ku7 it-chhe3 e5 kha-khau3 chhiu2-khau3 chit8 e7 theh8 ke3 chhiu2 liam5-piN oe7 hiau2 pak. Chit8 pai2 pian-kai3 bo5 an-cheng7, kok ong5 khi2 peng khi3 peng5, tiau3 sai-hu7 tiam3 kun-iaN5 chu3 ke-si. Chit8 mi5 chhat8 peng lai5, sai-hu7 hou7 in liah8--khi3, eng7 thih-khau3 pak8 i e5 kha. Sai-hu7 tai7-seng bo5 liah8 choe3 iau3-kin2, siuN7 bo5 lang5 ti7-teh e5 si5, tek-khak oe7 thau2 khui thau chau2. Jit8 am3, kou3-siu2 e5 lang5 khi3, sai-hu7 beh thau2 sou2 pak8 e5 lian7, bong chit8 khoan5 ke3 chit8 khoan5, long2 bo5 chit8 sou2-chai7 thau2 oe7 khui, in-ui7 si7 pun2-sin sou2 choe3--e5, bin7 liam5-piN lek-sek, chai bo5 chau2 chhut e5 ng3-bang7, chiah thou2-khui3 ka-ki7 choe3 ka-ki7 siu7. 
  Se3-kan lang5 kiaN5 tak8 hang7 e5 choe7-giat8, kau3 be2 tek-khak u7 hap8-gi5 e5 po3-eng3. Lo2 Chu2 kong2, “Ho2 phaiN2 e5 po3-eng3, chhin-chhiuN7 iaN2 te3 heng5.” In-ui7 heng5 siaN2 khoan2, iaN2 iah8 si7 an2-ni. Kho2-sioh se3-kan lang5 hou7 ka-ki7 choe3 e5 choe7-giat8 sou2 tiN5, tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 hou7 ka-ki7 choe3 e5 heng5-ku7 sou2 pak8, bo5 hoat-tou7 thang thoat-li7, kiam2 bo5 kho2 siong--mah? 
  Kiu3 Chu2 lai5 se3-kan, choan-choan chin2-kiu3 se3-kan lang5 thoat-li7 choe7-bang7. Sou2-i2 Seng3-keng kong2, “Ki5-to2 Chu2 e5 mia5 e5 tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3.” ChaiN2-iuN7 se3-kan lang5 iau2-ku2 m7 sin3. 
  Ia5-sou Ki-tok. 
  E7-toe2 saN e5 toe5-bak8, hut-jian5 khoaN3--kiN3 chhin-chhiuN7 bo5 siaN2 hun-piat, na7 soe3-ji7 siuN7, chiu7 toa7-toa7 bo5 saN-tang5. 
  1. KI-TOK SI7 CHIT8 E5 KIU3 CHU2 
  Chit toe5 put-ko3 kong2 Ki-tok si7 Kiu3 Chu2 na7-tiaN7, chong2-si7 bo5 siong5-se3 kong2 si7 sim2-mih8 ho7 Kiu3 Chu2, a2-si7 chi7-chui7 e5 Kiu3 Chu2. ThiaN-kiN3 chit ku3--e5, phah-sng3 Ki-tok sui-bong2 si7 Kiu3 Chu2, na7 si7 boe7 koat-toan3 tau3-ti2 kap goa2 u7 siaN2 koan-he7? An2-ni chit toe5 si7 hou5-hun7 e5 oe7. 
