  In-ui7 chai lin2 siu7-siok8 thoat-chhut tui3 chou2-kong sou2 liu5-thoan5 khang-khang e5 kiaN5-choe3, m7-si7 eng7 oe7 pai7-hoai7 e5 mih8, hek8-si7 gun5, a2-si7 kim; si7 eng7 po2-huih. (I Pi2-tek 1:18.) 
  Tok8-tok8 sin3 hit-e5 chheng put-khian5 e5 lang5 choe3 gi7--e5, i e5 sin3 chiu7 ka7 i sng3 choe3 gi7. (Lo5-ma2 4:5.) 
  Sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou, li2 kap li2 e5 ke tek-khak tit-tioh8 kiu3. (Su3-tou5 Heng5-toan7 16:31.) 
  Tioh8 chai lan2 lang5 chun5 sim kiaN5 tai7-chi3, sui-bong2 chap8 hun7 u7 kau2 hun7 hap8 to7-li2, chong2-si7 beh tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 hoaN-hi2 chiap-lap8, chiu7 tioh8 oa2-kho3 Ki-tok i2-keng choe3 chiaN5 e5 kong-lo5. In-ui7 lang5 tioh8 ka-ki7 chai bo5 tek-heng7 bo5 chai5-leng5, seng5-sim sin3-hok8 Kiu3 Chu2, jian5-au7 it-chhe3 e5 gian5-heng7 chiah oe7 hap8 to7-li2, chit ho7 khiam-hu sin3-giong2 e5 sim kio3 choe3 “To7-sim.” U7 to7-sim chiah u7 ho2 kiat-ko2, bo5 lun7 ti3-sek, gu5-gong7, gau5, put-siau3 long2-chong2 si7 an2-ni. Chong2 lai5 kong2, to7-sim si7 kun-pun2, ho2 phin2-heng7 si7 ki-hioh8, eng7 Ki-tok kiu3-siok8 e5 un choe3 khi2-in, chiah eng7 ho2 phin2-heng7 choe3 kiat-ko2 tek-khak bo5 chho3-gou7, na7 eng7 ho2 phin2-heng7 choe3 khi2-in, iah8 ng3-bang7 tit kiu3 choe3 kiat-ko2, chiu7 sou2 siuN7 kui khang-khang. 
